OL,3,CSex offender has sentence increased
OL,4,Cafter attacking women in Manchester
OL,6,FA man who sexually assaulted multiple
OL,7,Fyoung women and girls under a
OL,8,FManchester underpass has had his
OL,9,Fsentence increased after senior judges
OL,10,Fruled his original punishment was too
OL,11,Flenient.
OL,13,FRobert Emmerson, 40, targeted victims
OL,14,Fas young as 13 between November 2023
OL,15,Fand April 2024, exposing himself and
OL,16,Flaunching physical attacks near the
OL,17,FMancunian Way.
