OL,3,CSex offender has sentence increased
OL,4,Cafter attacking women in Manchester
OL,6,FThe women, most of whom were students,
OL,7,Fwere approached while walking alone in
OL,8,Fremote locations. Several were wearing
OL,9,Fheadphones at the time and unaware of
OL,10,FEmmerson until he confronted them.
OL,12,FVictims described being chased, pinned
OL,13,Fto the ground and groped. One said he
OL,14,Floomed over her "like a bear", while
OL,15,Fothers recalled him grinning during
OL,16,Fthe attacks.
OL,18,FEmmerson, from Wythenshawe, denied all
OL,19,Fcharges but was convicted by a jury in
OL,20,FOctober 2023. He was sentenced to four-
OL,21,Fand-a-half years in prison in January.
