OL,6,FHowever, the case was referred to the
OL,7,FCourt of Appeal in London by the
OL,8,FSolicitor General, who argued the
OL,9,Fsentence did not reflect the
OL,10,Fseriousness of the offences.
OL,12,FFollowing a hearing on Thursday 25
OL,13,FApril, three senior judges increased
OL,14,FEmmerson's sentence to seven years in
OL,15,Fcustody, with an additional three
OL,16,Fyears on licence after release.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
