OL,3,CSex offender has sentence increased
OL,4,Cafter attacking women in Manchester
OL,6,FGemma White KC, representing the
OL,7,FSolicitor General, told the court:
OL,8,F"They were all young ladies in a
OL,9,Fremote location. They had headphones
OL,10,Fon so would not have been aware of
OL,11,Ftheir surroundings. It is highly
OL,12,Flikely that this offender poses a high
OL,13,Frisk of both emotional and sexual harm
OL,14,Fto children, especially females."
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Police said
OL,17,FEmmerson was identified through DNA,
OL,18,FCCTV and a public appeal for
OL,19,Finformation.
