OL,6,FThe court also heard that Emmerson had
OL,7,Fprevious convictions for stalking and
OL,8,Findecent exposure in 2015.
OL,10,FDefending, Joshua Bowker said the
OL,11,Fsentencing judge had considered both
OL,12,Faggravating and mitigating factors,
OL,13,Fincluding the passage of time since
OL,14,Fthe offences and Emmerson's troubled
OL,15,Fbackground.
OL,17,FBut Lord Justice Edis, sitting with
OL,18,FMrs Justice Stacey and Judge Usha
OL,19,FKaru, said Emmerson's refusal to admit
OL,20,Fhis crimes left "limited" scope for
OL,21,Frehabilitation.
