OL,3,CSex offender has sentence increased
OL,4,Cafter attacking women in Manchester
OL,6,FLord Justice Edis said: "That serious
OL,7,Fconsequence of offending may resolve
OL,8,Fin some cases, but in many, if not
OL,9,Fall, it will leave a lifelong legacy
OL,10,Fof fear and harm in places where they
OL,11,Fought to feel safe."
OL,13,FFollowing the hearing, Solicitor
OL,14,FGeneral Lucy Rigby KC MP said: I was
OL,15,Fsickened and angered to read of the
OL,16,Foffenders numerous sexual assaults
OL,17,Fagainst women and girls.
