OL,6,F"The increased sentence clearly shows
OL,7,Fthat sex offenders will be brought to
OL,8,Fjustice and face the penalty they
OL,9,Fdeserve. My thoughts today are with
OL,10,Fthe young women attacked by Emmerson."
OL,12,FShe added that the government is
OL,13,Fcommitted to halving violence against
OL,14,Fwomen and girls within the next decade
OL,15,Fas part of its Plan for Change.
